.TH "STX FETCH" "1" "2026-04-20" "0.2.0" "stx fetch Manual"
.SH NAME
stx\-fetch \- Fetch daily-adjusted OHLCV for symbols...
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B stx fetch
[OPTIONS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Fetch daily-adjusted OHLCV for symbols into the local cache.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-cache\-dir\fP DIRECTORY
Root for raw/ and canonical/.  [default: data]
.TP
\fB\-\-symbols\fP TEXT
Ticker symbols (repeatable). Default: pilot universe.
.TP
\fB\-\-refresh\fP
Re-download and overwrite canonical CSV.
